# Deploy & smoke (API)

- GitLab CI: `./mvnw test` → Docker build/push ECR → ECS deploy → `scripts/smoke-api.py`
- Smoke verifies `/health`, `/api/v1/status`, both `/api/fishing/*/status` (biteScore 0–100)
- Docker: Java 26, `--enable-native-access=ALL-UNNAMED` for Netty/WebClient
- Pipeline failure after deploy = investigate ECS service `portfolio-api-5b60` before changing frontend
- Full detail: `AGENTS.md` and `README.md` → Deployment & smoke tests
